<lb n="0439c02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0439c03" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 983A [cf. Nos. 982, 984, 985]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0439c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0439018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】仁和寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此軌宋元二本缺，〔佛說〕－【明】【乙】</note><note n="0439018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】，【原】麗本，【甲】仁和寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此軌宋元二本缺</note><app n="0439018"><lem wit="【大】">佛<note n="0439019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝母【聖】【甲】＊</note><note n="0439019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">說【大】＊，母【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0439019"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">母</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0439018" type="rest" place="foot">【原】麗本，【甲】仁和寺藏古寫本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此軌宋元二本缺</note>大孔雀明王畫像壇場儀
<lb n="0439c05" ed="T"/><note n="0439020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＋（法）【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">軌【大】，軌法【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439020"><lem wit="【大】">軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">軌法</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0439c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0439c07" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0439021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（開府…寺）三十七字＝（唐北天竺）四字【明】【乙】，（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺）十字【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…寺）三十七字【大】，唐北天竺【明】【乙】，特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺【聖】【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="37" n="0439021"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0439c08" ed="T"/>肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司
<lb n="0439c09" ed="T"/>空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善
<lb n="0439c10" ed="T"/>寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">唐北天竺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺</rdg></app>三藏沙<note n="0439022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0439022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門【大】，門大廣智【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0439022"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】">門大廣智</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0439c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0439c1101">佛告阿難陀。若諸世間所有災禍逼惱。刀兵
<lb n="0439c12" ed="T"/>飢饉亢旱疾疫。四百四病憂<note n="0439023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惱＝苦【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惱【大】，苦【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439023"><lem wit="【大】">惱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">苦</rdg></app>鬪諍。及八萬
<lb n="0439c13" ed="T"/>四千鬼魅嬈惱有情。所求世間出世間勝願
<lb n="0439c14" ed="T"/>多有障礙者。<note n="0439024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">皆＝背【聖】</note><note n="0439024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，背【聖】</note><app n="0439024"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">背</rdg></app>由無始已來貪愛無明。虛妄
<lb n="0439c15" ed="T"/>分別三毒煩惱。不了實相積集不善。<note n="0439025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">感招＝敢柖【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">感招【大】，敢柖【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439025"><lem wit="【大】">感招</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">敢柖</rdg></app>如
<lb n="0439c16" ed="T"/>是種種災難。</p>
<lb n="0439c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0439c1701">阿難陀是故我今為彼讀誦佛母大孔雀明王
<lb n="0439c18" ed="T"/><note n="0439026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝終【聖】</note><note n="0439026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，終【聖】</note><app n="0439026"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">終</rdg></app>者。<note n="0439027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及一切災厄眾生〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0439027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及一切災厄眾生【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0439027"><lem wit="【大】">及一切災厄眾生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。復說畫像法及建
<lb n="0439c19" ed="T"/>立道場供養儀軌。若依此法轉讀是經。一切
<lb n="0439c20" ed="T"/>災難皆得消除。所有願求隨意滿足。阿難陀
<lb n="0439c21" ed="T"/>若有苦惱災難起時。或彼國王及諸王子大
<lb n="0439c22" ed="T"/>臣妃后。及苾芻苾芻尼善男子善女人等。為
<lb n="0439c23" ed="T"/>除災故。或於王宮或於勝地。或於清淨伽藍
<lb n="0439c24" ed="T"/>或隨本所居宅舍。依法淨地掘深一肘。除去
<lb n="0439c25" ed="T"/>瓦礫地中穢物。填滿淨土築令平正。其土本
<pb n="0440a" xml:id="T19.0983A.0440a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0440a01" ed="T"/>淨却用填之。若土有餘其地殊勝。應<note n="0440001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">泥拭＝埿穢【聖】，埿拭【甲】</note><note n="0440001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥拭【大】，埿穢【聖】，埿拭【甲】</note><app n="0440001"><lem wit="【大】">泥拭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">埿穢</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">埿拭</rdg></app>清
<lb n="0440a02" ed="T"/>淨建立道場作五肘方壇。高四指量三重布
<lb n="0440a03" ed="T"/>位。或以彩畫或用五色粉成。於內院中<note n="0440002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔心〕－【明】</note><note n="0440002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0440002"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0440a04" ed="T"/>畫八葉蓮華。於蓮華<note n="0440003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔胎〕－【明】</note><note n="0440003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">胎【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0440003"><lem wit="【大】">胎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>上畫佛母大孔雀明
<lb n="0440a05" ed="T"/>王菩薩。頭向東方白色。著白<note n="0440004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">繒＝增【聖】</note><note n="0440004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">繒【大】，增【聖】</note><app n="0440004"><lem wit="【大】">繒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">增</rdg></app>輕衣。頭冠
<lb n="0440a06" ed="T"/><note n="0440005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瓔珞＝纓絡【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瓔珞【大】，纓絡【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440005"><lem wit="【大】">瓔珞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">纓絡</rdg></app>耳<note n="0440006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">璫＝蟷【聖】</note><note n="0440006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">璫【大】，蟷【聖】</note><app n="0440006"><lem wit="【大】">璫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">蟷</rdg></app>臂釧種種莊嚴。乘金色孔雀<note n="0440007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔王〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440007"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。
<lb n="0440a07" ed="T"/>結跏趺坐白蓮華上。<note n="0440008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔或青綠花上〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或青綠花上【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440008"><lem wit="【大】">或青<note n="0440009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綠＝蓮【明】【乙】</note><note n="0440009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綠【大】，蓮【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440009"><lem wit="【大】">綠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">蓮</rdg></app>花上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。住慈悲
<lb n="0440a08" ed="T"/>相有四臂。右邊第一手執開敷蓮華。第二手
<lb n="0440a09" ed="T"/>持俱緣果<note place="inline">其果狀<note n="0440010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0440010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，〔－〕【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440010"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>似水苽</note>左邊第一手當心掌持吉
<lb n="0440a10" ed="T"/>祥菓<note n="0440011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如桃李形〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如桃李形【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">如桃<note n="0440012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">李＝子ヵ【乙】</note><note n="0440012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">李【大】，子【考偽-乙】</note><app n="0440012"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">李</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="correctionRemark">子</rdg></app>形</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>第二手執三五莖孔雀尾。從佛母
<lb n="0440a11" ed="T"/>右邊右旋。周匝蓮華葉上。畫七佛世尊。從微
<lb n="0440a12" ed="T"/>鉢尸如來<note n="0440013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（次第布列）＋乃【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃【大】，次第布列乃【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440013"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">次第布列乃</rdg></app>至釋迦及慈氏菩薩等。皆<note n="0440014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頭＝顧【聖】</note><note n="0440014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頭【大】，顧【聖】</note><app n="0440014"><lem wit="【大】">頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">顧</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440a13" ed="T"/>向外坐各住定相。至西北角第八葉上。畫慈
<lb n="0440a14" ed="T"/>氏菩薩。左手執軍持右手揚掌向外作<note n="0440015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔施〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440015"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無
<lb n="0440a15" ed="T"/>畏勢。又於蓮華葉外。內院四方畫四辟支佛。
<lb n="0440a16" ed="T"/>皆作佛形頂有肉髻亦住定相。<note n="0440016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔又於…從〕十字－【聖】</note><note n="0440016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（又於…從）十字【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app cb:word-count="10" n="0440016"><lem wit="【大】">又於四隅畫
<lb n="0440a17" ed="T"/>四大聲聞。從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>東北隅<note n="0440017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔畫〕－【聖】</note><note n="0440017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畫【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app n="0440017"><lem wit="【大】">畫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿難陀。次東南隅
<lb n="0440a18" ed="T"/>畫羅睺羅。次西南隅畫舍利弗。次西北隅
<lb n="0440a19" ed="T"/>畫大目<note n="0440018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">揵＝乾【明】【聖】【甲】＊</note><note n="0440018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">揵【大】＊，乾【明】【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440018"><lem wit="【大】">揵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】">乾</rdg></app>連。皆著<app type="star" corresp="#0440018"><lem wit="【大】">揵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】">乾</rdg></app>陀袈裟偏袒右臂。此
<lb n="0440a20" ed="T"/>皆中院。次第二院畫八方天王并諸眷屬。東
<lb n="0440a21" ed="T"/>方畫帝釋天王。執金剛杵與諸天眾圍遶。次
<lb n="0440a22" ed="T"/>東南方畫火<note n="0440019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＋（王）【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，天王【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440019"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">天王</rdg></app>。左手執軍持右手施無畏。與
<lb n="0440a23" ed="T"/>五通苦行仙眾圍遶。次南方畫焰摩天王。執
<lb n="0440a24" ed="T"/>焰摩幢。與焰摩<note n="0440020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔界〕－【乙】</note><note n="0440020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">界【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0440020"><lem wit="【大】">界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0440021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔鬼〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬼【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440021"><lem wit="【大】">鬼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>眾圍遶次西南方畫
<lb n="0440a25" ed="T"/>羅剎<note n="0440022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＝主【明】【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，主【明】【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440022"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】">主</rdg></app>執刀。與諸羅剎眾圍遶。次西方畫
<lb n="0440a26" ed="T"/>水<note n="0440023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＋（王）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0440023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，天王【校異-乙】</note><app n="0440023"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">天王</rdg></app>。持羂索。與諸龍眾圍遶。次西北方畫
<lb n="0440a27" ed="T"/>風天王。執幢幡。與諸持明仙眾圍遶。次北
<lb n="0440a28" ed="T"/>方畫多聞天王。執<note n="0440024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶棒＝實持【聖】</note><note n="0440024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶棒【大】，實持【聖】</note><app n="0440024"><lem wit="【大】">寶棒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">實持</rdg></app>。與諸藥叉眾圍遶。
<lb n="0440a29" ed="T"/>次東北方畫伊舍那天。執三戟叉。與諸步多
<pb n="0440b" xml:id="T19.0983A.0440b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0440b01" ed="T"/>鬼眾圍遶。此皆<note n="0440025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是〕－【乙】</note><note n="0440025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0440025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>第二院。次第三院從東
<lb n="0440b02" ed="T"/>北隅。右旋周匝畫二十八大藥叉將。各與諸
<lb n="0440b03" ed="T"/>鬼神眾圍遶。及畫宿曜十二宮神。次第三院
<lb n="0440b04" ed="T"/>外周匝。用香泥塗<note n="0440026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飾＝拭【明】【甲】【乙】，滅【聖】</note><note n="0440026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飾【大】，拭【明】【甲】【乙】，滅【聖】</note><app n="0440026"><lem wit="【大】">飾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">拭</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">滅</rdg></app>。布以荷葉。<note n="0440027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔葉〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440027"><lem wit="【大】">葉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>上<note n="0440028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔安〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440028"><lem wit="【大】">安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b05" ed="T"/>置供養食<note n="0440029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">食＝器【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0440029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，器【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440029"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】">器</rdg></app>所謂乳<note n="0440030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麋＝度【聖】</note><note n="0440030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麋【大】，度【聖】</note><app n="0440030"><lem wit="【大】">麋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">度</rdg></app>酪飯<note n="0440031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（飲）＋食【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0440031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，飲食【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0440031"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】">飲食</rdg></app>果子等。皆
<lb n="0440b06" ed="T"/>以阿波羅<note n="0440032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">爾＝<g ref="#CB14031"/>【明】【乙】＊</note><note n="0440032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾【大】＊，<g ref="#CB14031"/>【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0440032"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><g ref="#CB14031"/></rdg></app>多明王真言。加持香水散灑。布
<lb n="0440b07" ed="T"/>列四邊供養。及以諸<note n="0440033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">漿＝將水【聖】</note><note n="0440033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漿【大】，將水【聖】</note><app n="0440033"><lem wit="【大】">漿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">將水</rdg></app><note n="0440034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沙＝砂【明】【聖】【乙】</note><note n="0440034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙【大】，砂【明】【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0440034"><lem wit="【大】">沙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【乙】">砂</rdg></app>糖石蜜石榴蜜
<lb n="0440b08" ed="T"/>漿等而奉獻之。壇上散白色花於四角置<note n="0440035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【聖】【甲】＊</note><note n="0440035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酥【大】＊，蘇【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440035"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b09" ed="T"/>燈四盞。四門各置二淨器滿盛香水。於壇東
<lb n="0440b10" ed="T"/>安佛母大孔雀明王像。其畫像法如前畫壇。
<lb n="0440b11" ed="T"/><note n="0440036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝准【聖】</note><note n="0440036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】，准【聖】</note><app n="0440036"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">准</rdg></app>不安界道即<note n="0440037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝界【聖】</note><note n="0440037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，界【聖】</note><app n="0440037"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">界</rdg></app>。中院聖眾燒沈香和<note n="0440038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔香〕－【甲】</note><note n="0440038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0440038"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b12" ed="T"/>等供養。東方天眾應燒<note n="0440039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">白＝自【聖】</note><note n="0440039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白【大】，自【聖】</note><app n="0440039"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">自</rdg></app>膠香而為供養。南
<lb n="0440b13" ed="T"/>方天眾以紫鑛芥子<note n="0440040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及〕－【聖】</note><note n="0440040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app n="0440040"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>鹽相和燒之供養。西
<lb n="0440b14" ed="T"/>方天眾以<app type="star" corresp="#0440035"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>和安<note n="0440041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝息【明】【乙】</note><note n="0440041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉【大】，息【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440041"><lem wit="【大】">悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">息</rdg></app>香燒<note n="0440042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之供…眾〕七字－【聖】</note><note n="0440042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（之供…眾）七字【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app cb:word-count="7" n="0440042"><lem wit="【大】">之供養。北方天
<lb n="0440b15" ed="T"/>眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>應燒薰陸香而供養<note n="0440043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之〕－【甲】</note><note n="0440043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0440043"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。持<note n="0440044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＝讀【聖】</note><note n="0440044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，讀【聖】</note><app n="0440044"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">讀</rdg></app>者於壇西
<lb n="0440b16" ed="T"/><note n="0440045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔面〕－【明】【乙】</note><note n="0440045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">面【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】</note><app n="0440045"><lem wit="【大】">面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。敷茅薦為座。或坐<note n="0440046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">卑＝厘【明】，厚【聖】，庳【乙】</note><note n="0440046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">卑【大】，厘【明】，厚【聖】，庳【乙】</note><app n="0440046"><lem wit="【大】">卑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">厘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">厚</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">庳</rdg></app>脚床子。嚴飾經案
<lb n="0440b17" ed="T"/>置於壇前。以諸香花供養經卷。應如是布列。
<lb n="0440b18" ed="T"/>轉讀經者可三<note n="0440047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0440047" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->人【大】＊，〔－〕【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0440047"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五人<note n="0440048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔乃至〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃至【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440048"><lem wit="【大】">乃至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七人。更<note n="0440049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">替＝贊【聖】</note><note n="0440049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">替【大】，贊【聖】</note><app n="0440049"><lem wit="【大】">替</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">贊</rdg></app>相
<lb n="0440b19" ed="T"/>續晝夜不令經聲間斷。<note n="0440050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔要在…場〕六十二字－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（要在…場）六十二字【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="62" n="0440050"><lem wit="【大】">要在絕語言。除數內
<lb n="0440b20" ed="T"/>一人明閑教法。呪師指撝取與<note n="0440051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">祇＝祗【明】</note><note n="0440051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祇【大】，祗【明】</note><app n="0440051"><lem wit="【大】">祇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">祗</rdg></app>對。作法
<lb n="0440b21" ed="T"/>結印啟請賢聖。餘人但當至心讀經。唯在遍
<lb n="0440b22" ed="T"/>數多。慇重發願依三十七尊禮懺。三時或六
<lb n="0440b23" ed="T"/>時。其道場</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>或一日或二日三日乃至七日。一
<lb n="0440b24" ed="T"/>切災禍悉皆殄滅。除不至心。轉經者或在家
<lb n="0440b25" ed="T"/>人或是出家人。每日澡浴清淨著新淨衣。<note n="0440052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">初＝禍【聖】</note><note n="0440052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">初【大】，禍【聖】</note><app n="0440052"><lem wit="【大】">初</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">禍</rdg></app>
<lb n="0440b26" ed="T"/>起首時對道場前。虔誠一心禮諸聖眾。先以
<lb n="0440b27" ed="T"/>印契真言。依教請召一切佛菩薩及諸<note n="0440053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝大【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天【大】，大【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440053"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">大</rdg></app>眾。
<lb n="0440b28" ed="T"/>如法供養。說所求事慇懃啟告。願垂加護。普
<lb n="0440b29" ed="T"/>為一切苦難眾生。廣發大願。然後結跏趺坐
<pb n="0440c" xml:id="T19.0983A.0440c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0440c01" ed="T"/>以塗香塗手。先結三昧耶印。二手<note n="0440054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔右〕－【聖】</note><note n="0440054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app n="0440054"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>押左外
<lb n="0440c02" ed="T"/>相叉作拳。直竪二中指頭相<note n="0440055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝跓【聖】【甲】＊</note><note n="0440055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄【大】＊，跓【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0440055"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">跓</rdg></app>即成。結印當
<lb n="0440c03" ed="T"/>心誦三昧耶真言七遍真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0440c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0440c0401" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0440056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引一）細註【明】【乙】＊</note><note n="0440056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵【大】＊，唵(引一)【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0440056"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>三<note n="0440057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】【乙】，〔去〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，去聲【明】【乙】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440057"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0440058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麼＝摩【聖】＊</note><note n="0440058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼【大】＊，摩【聖】＊</note><app n="0440058"><lem wit="【大】">麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">摩</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0440059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＋（聲）【明】【乙】，（二）【聖】</note><note n="0440059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，上聲【明】【乙】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->上二【聖】</note><app n="0440059"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">上聲</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">上二</rdg></app></note>野娑怛鍐<note place="inline"><note n="0440060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三合＝二合三【聖】</note><note n="0440060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三合【大】，二合三【聖】</note><app n="0440060"><lem wit="【大】">三合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">二合三</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0440c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0440c0501">即以此印加持自身四處。所謂心額<note n="0440061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喉頂＝唯項【聖】</note><note n="0440061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喉頂【大】，唯項【聖】</note><app n="0440061"><lem wit="【大】">喉頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">唯項</rdg></app>頂
