<lb n="0440c07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0440c0701">次結金剛鉤菩薩印。</p>
<lb n="0440c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0440c0801">准前三昧耶印。以二頭指屈如鉤向身<note n="0440062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">招＋（之）【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0440062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">招【大】，招之【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0440062"><lem wit="【大】">招</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">招之</rdg></app>。不
<lb n="0440c09" ed="T"/>間斷誦真言七遍。<note n="0440063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">普＝善【聖】</note><note n="0440063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普【大】，善【聖】</note><app n="0440063"><lem wit="【大】">普</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">善</rdg></app>召諸佛菩薩諸天鬼神
