<lb n="0441a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0441a1401">次結佛母大孔雀明王印。</p>
<lb n="0441a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0441a1501">二手右押左內相叉。二大指二小指。各直竪
<lb n="0441a16" ed="T"/>頭相<app type="star" corresp="#0440055"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">跓</rdg></app>即成。結<note n="0441020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【聖】</note><note n="0441020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，〔－〕【聖】</note><app n="0441020"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>當心誦真言七遍。如<note n="0441021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">前＝上【明】【乙】</note><note n="0441021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，上【明】【乙】</note><app n="0441021"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">上</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a17" ed="T"/>以印加持四<note n="0441022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處＝虔【明】</note><note n="0441022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">處【大】，虔【明】</note><app n="0441022"><lem wit="【大】">處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">虔</rdg></app>頂上散印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0441a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0441a1801" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0440056"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0440058"><lem wit="【大】">麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">摩</rdg></app>庾<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0441023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】，羅【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441023"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note><note n="0441024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訖＝說【聖】</note><note n="0441024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訖【大】，說【聖】</note><app n="0441024"><lem wit="【大】">訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">說</rdg></app>蘭<note place="inline">二合<note n="0441025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【聖】【甲】＊</note><note n="0441025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，〔－〕【聖】【甲】＊</note><app n="0441025"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>帝<note n="0441026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【明】【甲】</note><note n="0441026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【明】【甲】</note><app n="0441026"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合<app type="star" corresp="#0441025"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0441a19" ed="T"/><note n="0441027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝訶引二【明】【乙】，賀引【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶引二【明】【乙】，賀引【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441027"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">訶引二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0441a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0441a2001">次捧香爐奉獻啟請。告<note n="0441028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔白〕－【明】【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白【大】，〔－〕【明】【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441028"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>聖眾說所求事。如
<lb n="0441a21" ed="T"/>是依法請召供養已。然後起悲愍心。為拔濟
<lb n="0441a22" ed="T"/>眾生苦難故。轉讀此經。每日中前換<note n="0441029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">諸供＝供養【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸供【大】，供養【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441029"><lem wit="【大】">諸供</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">供養</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a23" ed="T"/>物。應結阿<note n="0441030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波＝婆【聖】</note><note n="0441030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波【大】，婆【聖】</note><app n="0441030"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">婆</rdg></app>羅<app type="star" corresp="#0440032"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><g ref="#CB14031"/></rdg></app>多明王印誦本真言。以
<lb n="0441a24" ed="T"/>印頂上左旋一匝。暫解其界換供養已。即如
<lb n="0441a25" ed="T"/>前次第再迎請結界如是依教供養轉讀此
<lb n="0441a26" ed="T"/>經。所有災難<note n="0441031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亢＝呪【聖】</note><note n="0441031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亢【大】，呪【聖】</note><app n="0441031"><lem wit="【大】">亢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">呪</rdg></app>旱疾疫。鬼魅厭禱惡毒災
<lb n="0441a27" ed="T"/>障。種種苦難必得除滅。所有祈願無不遂心。
<lb n="0441a28" ed="T"/>我<note n="0441032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＋（今）【聖】</note><note n="0441032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，已今【聖】</note><app n="0441032"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">已今</rdg></app>廣說畫像壇場供養儀軌竟。若不<note n="0441033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辦＝辯【明】，辨【甲】</note><note n="0441033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦【大】，辯【明】，辨【甲】</note><app n="0441033"><lem wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">辯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">辨</rdg></app>
<lb n="0441a29" ed="T"/>如是塗畫壇場。或有急速災難<note n="0441034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＋（時）【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0441034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，至時【聖】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441034"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】【乙】">至時</rdg></app>。可隨自
<pb n="0441b" xml:id="T19.0983A.0441b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0441b01" ed="T"/>力分於一淨處。以瞿摩夷塗地作一<note n="0441035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔肘〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0441035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肘【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441035"><lem wit="【大】">肘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>方壇。
<lb n="0441b02" ed="T"/><note n="0441036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隨＋（意）【聖】【乙】</note><note n="0441036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨【大】，隨意【聖】【乙】</note><app n="0441036"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【乙】">隨意</rdg></app><note n="0441037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＝畢【甲】</note><note n="0441037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，畢【甲】</note><app n="0441037"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">畢</rdg></app>大小。<note n="0441038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">磨＝麼【聖】</note><note n="0441038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">磨【大】，麼【聖】</note><app n="0441038"><lem wit="【大】">磨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">麼</rdg></app>白檀香塗作圓壇。九位中安
<lb n="0441b03" ed="T"/>佛像。及以三五莖孔雀尾<note n="0441039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">竪＝賢【聖】</note><note n="0441039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竪【大】，賢【聖】</note><app n="0441039"><lem wit="【大】">竪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">賢</rdg></app>於壇<note n="0441040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（中）＋上【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，中上【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441040"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">中上</rdg></app>。隨時
<lb n="0441b04" ed="T"/>燒香散花乳<note n="0441041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">糜＝摩【聖】</note><note n="0441041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">糜【大】，摩【聖】</note><app n="0441041"><lem wit="【大】">糜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">摩</rdg></app>酪<note n="0441042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">等＝飲【聖】，飰【甲】</note><note n="0441042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等【大】，飲【聖】，飰【甲】</note><app n="0441042"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">飲</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">飰</rdg></app>供養聖眾。但虔誠一
<lb n="0441b05" ed="T"/>心轉讀此經。<note n="0441043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔或一遍〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或一遍【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441043"><lem wit="【大】">或一遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>或三遍乃至七遍。或一
<lb n="0441b06" ed="T"/>日或二日。一切厄難悉得消除。所有祈願皆
<lb n="0441b07" ed="T"/>得圓滿。</p>
<lb n="0441b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0441b0801">爾時阿難陀聞佛世尊。為當來<note n="0441044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔世〕－【聖】【甲】</note><note n="0441044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，〔－〕【聖】【甲】</note><app n="0441044"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一切苦難
<lb n="0441b09" ed="T"/>有情。說此讀誦大孔雀明王經法。頂戴受持
<lb n="0441b10" ed="T"/>禮佛而退。</p>
<lb n="0441b11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0441045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0441045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0441045"><lem wit="【大】">佛<app type="star" corresp="#0439019"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】【甲】">母</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大孔雀明王<note n="0441046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔畫像壇場〕－【甲】</note><note n="0441046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畫像壇場【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0441046"><lem wit="【大】">畫像壇場</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>儀軌<note n="0441047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法一）＋卷【聖】，（一）＋卷【甲】，〔卷〕－【乙】，乙本奧書曰貞享三年仲秋十一夜訓點了河南教興傳密沙門淨嚴四十有八元祿十六年正月二十五日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note><note n="0441047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">卷【大】，法一卷【聖】，一卷【甲】，〔－〕【乙】，乙本奧書曰貞享三年仲秋十一夜訓點了河南教興傳密沙門淨嚴四十有八元祿十六年正月二十五日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note><app n="0441047"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">卷</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><note place="inline">法一卷</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">一卷</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0441047" type="rest" place="foot">乙本奧書曰貞享三年仲秋十一夜訓點了河南教興傳密沙門淨嚴四十有八元祿十六年正月二十五日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
